inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let systemName = "library-management";
let timeFrame = 28d;
let topRequests=requests
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName
| where operation_Name != ""
| summarize Count = count() by operation_Name
| order by Count
| top 5 by Count
| project operation_Name
;
requests
| where operation_Name in (topRequests)
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName
| summarize avg(duration) by operation_Name, bin(timestamp, 7d)
| render timechart

content.PartTitle: Most Called Requests Duration Over Time (50th percentile)
content.Query:
let systemName = "library-management";
let timeFrame = 28d;
let topRequests=requests
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName or customDimensions.system_KubernetesNamespace == systemName
| where operation_Name != "" and operation_Name !startswith "PROCESS"
| summarize Count = count() by operation_Name
| order by Count
| top 6 by Count
| project operation_Name
;
requests
| where operation_Name in (topRequests)
| where success == true
| where timestamp > ago(timeFrame)
| where customDimensions["KubernetesNamespace"] == systemName or customDimensions.system_KubernetesNamespace == systemName
| summarize Duration=percentiles(duration, 50) by operation_Name, bin(timestamp, 7d)
| render timechart

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
requests
| where customDimensions["system_KubernetesNamespace"] == "preview-engine"
| where success == false
| join kind= inner (exceptions) on operation_Id
| project
    exceptionType = type,
    requestName = name,
    failedMethod = method,
    operation_Id,
    timestamp
| summarize ExampleOperationId=max(operation_Id), LastOcurrence=max(timestamp), count() by exceptionType, failedMethod, requestName
| order by count_

content.Query:
exceptions
| where timestamp > ago(7d)
| where tostring(customDimensions["system_SystemName"]) == "preview-engine"
| join kind= leftouter (requests) on operation_Id
| project 
    exceptionType = type,
    operation_Id,
    timestamp,
    failedMethod = method,
    requestName = name
| summarize 
    ExampleOperationId=max(operation_Id),
    LastOcurrence=max(timestamp),
    count() by exceptionType,
    failedMethod,
    requestName
| order by
    ExampleOperationId,
    count_

content.PartTitle: Top Exceptions in Library Management in the last 7 days
content.Query:
// Exceptions causing request failures 
// Find which exceptions led to failed requests in the past hour. 
let systemName = "library-management";
let since = ago(7d);
requests
| where timestamp > since
| where customDimensions.KubernetesNamespace == systemName or customDimensions.system_KubernetesNamespace == systemName
| where resultCode == 500
| where success == false
| join kind= inner (exceptions) on operation_Id
| project exceptionType = type, requestName = name, failedMethod = method, operation_Id, timestamp
| where exceptionType != "Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.DbUpdateConcurrencyException" 
or requestName startswith "PROCESS Failed"
| summarize ExampleOperationId=max(operation_Id),LastOcurrence=max(timestamp), count() by exceptionType, failedMethod, requestName
| order by count_
